#. <section class="sutta" id="sn3.6"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn3.6:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 3"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 3"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn3.6:0.2"
msgid "1. Paṭhamavagga"
msgstr "1. Shackles"

#. </p><h1>
#. VAR: 6. Appakasutta → appakāsuttaṃ (bj) | appakasuttaṃ (pts2)
msgctxt "sn3.6:0.3"
msgid "6. Appakasutta"
msgstr "6. Few"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="pts1ed" id="pts1ed1.74"></a>
#. <a class="pts2ed" id="pts2ed1.169"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn3.6:1.1"
msgid "Sāvatthinidānaṃ."
msgstr "At Sāvatthī."

msgctxt "sn3.6:1.2"
msgid "Ekamantaṃ nisinno kho rājā pasenadi kosalo bhagavantaṃ etadavoca:"
msgstr "Seated to one side, King Pasenadi said to the Buddha:"

msgctxt "sn3.6:1.3"
msgid ""
"“idha mayhaṃ, bhante, rahogatassa paṭisallīnassa evaṃ cetaso parivitakko "
"udapādi:"
msgstr "“Just now, sir, as I was in private retreat this thought came to mind."

msgctxt "sn3.6:1.4"
msgid ""
"‘appakā te sattā lokasmiṃ ye uḷāre uḷāre bhoge labhitvā na ceva majjanti, na "
"ca pamajjanti, na ca kāmesu gedhaṃ āpajjanti, na ca sattesu vippaṭipajjanti."
msgstr ""
"‘Few are the sentient beings in the world who, when they obtain luxury "
"possessions, don’t get indulgent and negligent, giving in to greed for "
"sensual pleasures, and doing the wrong thing by others."

msgctxt "sn3.6:1.5"
msgid ""
"Atha kho eteva bahutarā sattā lokasmiṃ ye uḷāre uḷāre bhoge labhitvā "
"majjanti ceva pamajjanti, ca kāmesu ca gedhaṃ āpajjanti, sattesu ca "
"vippaṭipajjantī’”ti."
msgstr ""
"There are many more who, when they obtain luxury possessions, do get "
"indulgent and negligent, giving in to greed for sensual pleasures, and doing "
"the wrong thing by others.’”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "sn3.6:2.1"
msgid "“Evametaṃ, mahārāja, evametaṃ, mahārāja."
msgstr ""
"“That’s so true, great king! That’s so true!” said the Buddha. And he "
"repeated the king’s statement, adding:"

msgctxt "sn3.6:2.2"
msgid ""
"Appakā te, mahārāja, sattā lokasmiṃ, ye uḷāre uḷāre bhoge labhitvā na ceva "
"majjanti, na ca pamajjanti, na ca kāmesu gedhaṃ āpajjanti, na ca sattesu "
"vippaṭipajjanti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn3.6:2.3"
msgid ""
"Atha kho eteva bahutarā sattā lokasmiṃ, ye uḷāre uḷāre bhoge labhitvā "
"majjanti ceva pamajjanti ca kāmesu ca gedhaṃ āpajjanti, sattesu ca "
"vippaṭipajjantī”ti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn3.6:2.4"
msgid "Idamavoca … pe …"
msgstr ""

#. </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "sn3.6:3.1"
msgid "“Sārattā kāmabhogesu,"
msgstr "“Full of desire for possessions and pleasures,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn3.6:3.2"
msgid "giddhā kāmesu mucchitā;"
msgstr "greedy, stupefied by sensual pleasures;"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn3.6:3.3"
msgid "Atisāraṃ na bujjhanti,"
msgstr "they don’t notice that they’ve gone too far,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn3.6:3.4"
msgid "migā kūṭaṃva oḍḍitaṃ;"
msgstr "like deer falling into a trap set out."

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn3.6:3.5"
msgid "Pacchāsaṃ kaṭukaṃ hoti,"
msgstr "It’ll be bitter later on;"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn3.6:3.6"
msgid "vipāko hissa pāpako”ti."
msgstr "for the result will be bad for them.”"
